ce:section.ce:para:
The Langmuir-Hinshelwood (L-H) model was used to determine the kinetics of IBU photodegradation, as well as pseudo-first order kinetics and apparent rate constants (k

                              app
                           ). The computed apparent rate constants for the TBrP-GQDs and InTBrP-GQDs photocatalysts were 0.0039 min−1 and 0.0092 min−1, respectively (Fig. 5b). The photocatalytic efficiency of the InTBrP-GQDs photocatalyst was three times that of the TBrP-GQDs photocatalyst. With InTBrP-GQDs photocatalyst being the most efficient photocatalyst between the two, all further experiments in the study were conducted using the InTBrP-GQDs photocatalyst.
